書（須附繕本）。　\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　11　　月　　30　　日\r\n                              書 記 官  梁高賓","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHEV/111%2c%e5%bd%b0%e7%b0%a1%2c545%2c20221130%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHEV,111,彰簡,545,20221130,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"彰簡","JNO":"545","JDATE":"20221130","JTITLE":"損害賠償"}